item.title: 272: Billionaires vs. The World (w/ Jim Di Bartolo)
item.description: Writer and illustrator Jim Di Bartolo joins DOOMED with Matt Binder for a discussion about the problem with billionaires, the discourse around the assassination of the United Healthcare CEO, his upcoming graphic novel "F*ck Billionaires" and more! (Episode from the 2/12/25 livestream show). Check out Jim's graphic novel: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/f-ckbillionaires/f-ck-billionaires - Support the show: http://www.patreon.com/mattbinder Feed: https://feeds.simplecast.com/QxmNZH68
